istent with those\nalready found in other Chandra and XMM-Newton observations of GX 13+1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Sep 2014 21:46:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Sep 2014 10:28:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
