 calculation is provided and an upper bound on the\ndata loss probability is obtained by posing the problem as a set avoidance\nproblem. Theoretical calculations are compared to simulation results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Sep 2014 15:12:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Apr 2015 12:50:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 May 2015 21:47:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2015 03:37:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-18"}
